==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[appropriatus]]'', past participle of ''[[appropriare]]'', from ''[[ad#Latin|ad]]'' + ''[[propriare]]'' to appropriate, from ''[[proprius]]'', one's own, proper.

