**[[IPA]]: /əˈprəʊpreɪt/ (''[[RP]]''), /əˈproʊpreɪt/ (''US'')
**[[SAMPA]]: /<tt>@"pr@UprieIt</tt>/ (''RP''), /<tt>@"proUpreIt</tt>/ (''US'')
**{{audio|en-us-appropriate-verb.ogg|Audio (US)}}
